<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>The Grand Book Club</title>
  <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url("/img/nn.jpg"); /* Optional background image */
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #333; /* Darker text for better contrast */
        }
    }

    /* Header */
        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #384b38; /* Night Blue */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #384b38;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;

        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #ffff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: black;
            
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background-color: #c89666; /* Light Yellow */
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            nav a {
                color: #384b38; /* Night Blue */
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
                font-weight: bold
            }

                nav a:hover {
                    background-color: #c1a77a; /* Lighter Yellow */
                    color: #fff;
                }

                nav a.active { /* Style for current page */
                    background-color: #384b38; /* Night Blue */
                    color: #fff;
                }





        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #384b38; /* Night Blue */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

    /* Main Content */
    main {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* About the Book Club */
    .about {
      background-color: #e1b382; /* Sand Tan */
      color: #333; /* Darker text for contrast */
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

      .about p {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.5; /* Improve readability */
      }

        /* Featured Books */
        .featured-books {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            background-color: #384b38;
        }

        .featured-book {
            background-color: #384b38;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            flex-basis: calc(50% - 20px); /* Adjusted width for each book */
            max-width: calc(50% - 20px); /* Adjusted max-width for responsiveness */
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding in the width calculation */
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

            .featured-book:hover {
                background-color: #e1b382;
            }

            .featured-book .featured-book-img {
                width: 50%;
                height: auto;
            }

        .featured-book-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 50%;
            height: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            color: #fff;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .featured-book-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

        .featured-book-author {
            font-style: italic;
        }


    
    /* Upcoming Events Section Heading */
    .event {
      background-color: #e1b382; /* Sand Tan */
      color: #333; /* Darker text for contrast */
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

      .event h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

    /* Sign Up Button */
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add some space after the button */
    }

      .cta button {
        padding: 15px 30px;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        background-color: #2d545e; /* Night Blue */
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }

        .cta button:hover {
          background-color: #12343b; /* Night Blue Shadow */
        }

    /* Social Media Icons */
    .social-media {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5; /* Light Grey */
    }

      .social-media a {
        margin: 0 10px;
        font-size: 1.5em;
        color: #2d545e; /* Night Blue */
        transition: color 0.3s;
      }

        .social-media a:hover {
          color: #12343b; /* Night Blue Shadow */
        }

    
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>The Bookish Circle</h1>
  </header>
    <nav>
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
        <a asp-controller="About" asp-action="Index">About Us</a>
        <a asp-controller="FeaturedBooks" asp-action="Index">Featured Books</a>
        <a asp-controller="Membership" asp-action="Index">Membership</a>
        <a asp-controller="SignUp" asp-action="Index">Sign up</a>
    </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="about">
      <p>The Bookish Circle is a community of passionate readers who love to discover new books and discuss them with others. We host regular meetings where members can share their thoughts on the latest reads, connect with fellow bookworms, and enjoy the company of other literature enthusiasts.</p>
    </section>

    <h2>Featured Books</h2>
    <section class="featured-books">
      <div class="featured-book">
                <img class="featured-book-img" src="~/img/acotar.jpg" alt="Book 1 Cover"  >
        <div class="featured-book-overlay">
                    <h3 class="featured-book-title">A Court of Thorns and Roses</h3>
          <p class="featured-book-author">Sarah J. Maas </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="featured-book">
                <img class="featured-book-img" src="~/img/i7.jpg" alt="Book 2 Cover"  >
                   <div class="featured-book-overlay">
                    <h3 class="featured-book-title">Things We Never Got Over</h3>
                    <p class="featured-book-author">Lucy Score</p>
                  </div>
      </div>
      </section>

    <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>
    <section class="event">
      <h3>Join us on 23rd April at 12:30 to discuss DIS.</h3>
      <p>Location: BSN 123</p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <button>Join the Club!</button>
    </section>

    <section class="social-media">
      <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
      <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
      <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i></a>
    </section>
  </main>

  
</body>
</html>
